-4.11.18-Ad-Tracking-300x158.webp 75w,\n/static/3157549ef3ed2a02f10af771720d86c0/cba1b/Image-4.11.18-Ad-Tracking-300x158.webp 150w,\n/static/3157549ef3ed2a02f10af771720d86c0/93dd2/Image-4.11.18-Ad-Tracking-300x158.webp 300w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 300px) 300px, 100vw"}]},"width":300,"height":181}}}}}},{"categories":{"nodes":[{"name":"Agency News"}]},"title":"Four Ways Marketing Provides Value","slug":"four-ways-marketing-provides-value","featuredImage":{"node":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/9d84d331d6be217897c9bac365d24015/e4495/4-Ways-Marketing-Provides-Value.png","srcSet":"/static/9d84d331d6be217897c9bac365d24015/5329f/4-Ways-Marketing-Provides-Value.png 300w,\n/static/9d84d331d6be217897c9bac365d24015/6d090/4-Ways-Marketing-Provides-Value.png 600w,\n/static/9d84d331d6be217897c9bac365d24015/e4495/4-Ways-Marketing-Provides-Value.png 1200w","sizes":"(min-width: 1200px) 1200px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/9d84d331d6be217897c9bac365d24015/93dd2/4-Ways-Marketing-Provides-Value.webp 300w,\n/static/9d84d331d6be217897c9bac365d24015/336f1/4-Ways-Marketing-Provides-Value.webp 600w,\n/static/9d84d331d6be217897c9bac365d24015/77a67/4-Ways-Marketing-Provides-Value.webp 1200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 1200px) 1200px, 100vw"}]},"width":1200,"height":723}}}}}}]}}]}},"pageContext":{"id":"cG9zdDoyMzUw","content":"<p style=\"margin-bottom: .75rem;\">Our industry is full of creatives waiting to share their craft and National Joke Day is a fun outlet to showcase their talents in a way we don’t normally get to see.  We’ve picked our favorite marketing joke thanks to <a href=\"https://www.hubspot.com/\">Hubspot</a>.</p>\n<p><span class=\"wp-image-2360 aligncenter inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:954px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:74.89539748953975%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/0b168dfdb18aaccbf29af8b7ad3dc326/a6236/joke-day-1200x900-1.png 239w,\n/static/0b168dfdb18aaccbf29af8b7ad3dc326/2dd4c/joke-day-1200x900-1.png 477w,\n/static/0b168dfdb18aaccbf29af8b7ad3dc326/cc0a2/joke-day-1200x900-1.png 954w,\n/static/0b168dfdb18aaccbf29af8b7ad3dc326/5ece7/joke-day-1200x900-1.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 954px) 100vw, 954px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 954px) 100vw, 954px\" srcSet=\"/static/0b168dfdb18aaccbf29af8b7ad3dc326/a6236/joke-day-1200x900-1.png 239w,\n/static/0b168dfdb18aaccbf29af8b7ad3dc326/2dd4c/joke-day-1200x900-1.png 477w,\n/static/0b168dfdb18aaccbf29af8b7ad3dc326/cc0a2/joke-day-1200x900-1.png 954w,\n/static/0b168dfdb18aaccbf29af8b7ad3dc326/5ece7/joke-day-1200x900-1.png 1200w\" src=\"/static/0b168dfdb18aaccbf29af8b7ad3dc326/cc0a2/joke-day-1200x900-1.png\" alt=\"National Joke Day 2017\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/0b168dfdb18aaccbf29af8b7ad3dc326/a6236/joke-day-1200x900-1.png 239w,\n/static/0b168dfdb18aaccbf29af8b7ad3dc326/2dd4c/joke-day-1200x900-1.png 477w,\n/static/0b168dfdb18aaccbf29af8b7ad3dc326/cc0a2/joke-day-1200x900-1.png 954w,\n/static/0b168dfdb18aaccbf29af8b7ad3dc326/5ece7/joke-day-1200x900-1.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 954px) 100vw, 954px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 954px) 100vw, 954px\" srcset=\"/static/0b168dfdb18aaccbf29af8b7ad3dc326/a6236/joke-day-1200x900-1.png 239w,\n/static/0b168dfdb18aaccbf29af8b7ad3dc326/2dd4c/joke-day-1200x900-1.png 477w,\n/static/0b168dfdb18aaccbf29af8b7ad3dc326/cc0a2/joke-day-1200x900-1.png 954w,\n/static/0b168dfdb18aaccbf29af8b7ad3dc326/5ece7/joke-day-1200x900-1.png 1200w\" src=\"/static/0b168dfdb18aaccbf29af8b7ad3dc326/cc0a2/joke-day-1200x900-1.png\" alt=\"National Joke Day 2017\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></p>\n<h2>Here are the jokes that didn’t make the cut.  Share with us your favorites on our <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ThePMGroup/\">Facebook</a> page.</h2>\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 1.75rem;\" id=\"marketersLightbulb\">\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: .75rem;\">How many marketers does it take to screw in a light bulb?</p>\n<p><img style=\"max-width:100%;width:480px\" class=\" inline-gatsby-image-wrapper\" loading=\"eager\" alt=\"Homer Simpson struggling with lightbulb\" src=\"/static/cb20177c03fa2e7f1080b30a80b8cbb3/homer-simpson-lightbulb.gif\" data-reactroot=\"\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: .75rem;\"><a href=\"https://giphy.com/gifs/season-6-the-simpsons-6x20-3orif0iFjZsYO3pDGg\">via GIPHY</a></p>\n<p><strong style=\"margin-bottom: .75rem;\">None – they’ve automated it</strong>\n</div>\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 1.75rem;\" id=\"browserCookies\">\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: .75rem;\">What does the new Chips Ahoy marketing director do her first day on the job?</p>\n<p><img style=\"max-width:100%;width:480px\" class=\" inline-gatsby-image-wrapper\" loading=\"eager\" alt=\"Browser cookies - Cookie Monster\" src=\"/static/2b531f53cba6aa60be96dc0221c7fba3/browser-cookies-monster.gif\" data-reactroot=\"\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: .75rem;\"><a href=\"https://giphy.com/gifs/o5oLImoQgGsKY\">via GIPHY</a></p>\n<p><strong style=\"margin-bottom: .75rem;\">Enable cookies.</strong>\n</div>\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 1.75rem;\" id=\"antiSocialMarketer\">\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: .75rem;\">What’s a personality trait of a bad marketer?</p>\n<p><img style=\"max-width:100%;width:267px\" class=\" inline-gatsby-image-wrapper\" loading=\"eager\" alt=\"Homer Simpson backing into hedge\" src=\"/static/221ef24d0c77f10cbde17a77171caf89/homer-simpson-bushes.gif\" data-reactroot=\"\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: .75rem;\"><a href=\"https://giphy.com/gifs/homer-simpson-the-simpsons-bush-4pMX5rJ4PYAEM\">via GIPHY</a></p>\n<p><strong style=\"margin-bottom: .75rem;\">Anti-social.</strong>\n</div>\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 1.75rem;\" id=\"marketingBounce\">\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: .75rem;\">Why did the marketer get off the trampoline?</p>\n<p><img style=\"max-width:100%;width:260px\" class=\" inline-gatsby-image-wrapper\" loading=\"eager\" alt=\"Dog on trampoline\" src=\"/static/2f36010ad7fcac7e9d721703cef8a02e/trampoline-dog.gif\" data-reactroot=\"\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: .75rem;\"><a href=\"https://giphy.com/gifs/cheezburger-dog-dogs-u0dFLjaRPlNdK\">via GIPHY</a></p>\n<p><strong style=\"margin-bottom: .75rem;\">He was worried about his bounce rate.</strong>\n</div>\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 1.75rem;\" id=\"marketerWideReceiver\">\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: .75rem;\">Why do marketers make such good wide receivers?</p>\n<p><img style=\"max-width:100%;width:480px\" class=\" inline-gatsby-image-wrapper\" loading=\"eager\" alt=\"Wide receiver\" src=\"/static/797fef692b704e2e8031d2a50acf262f/wide-receiver.gif\" data-reactroot=\"\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: .75rem;\"><a href=\"https://giphy.com/gifs/nfl-football-xUPGcB5L0TIfLrDH8c\">via GIPHY</a></p>\n<p><strong style=\"margin-bottom: .75rem;\">Because they always stay inbounds.</strong>\n</div>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: .75rem;\"><a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com\">About The PM Group</a>: The PM Group was founded in 1988. Over the past 30 years, the agency has continued to grow and is currently listed as San Antonio’s Largest Advertising Agency by the San Antonio Business Journal. The PM Group’s client roster spans numerous industries including automotive, CPG, entertainment and sports marketing, legal, business services, non-profit, real estate and fitness. In addition, the agency hosts an annual Charity Gala every February that to date has raised over $2.5 million for local San Antonio area non-profit organizations in the last 15 years! It is our way of giving back to the community that we so humbly serve.</p>\n","title":"5 Marketing Jokes That Didn’t Make the Cut","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"5 Marketing Jokes That Didn’t Make the Cut","url":"/5-marketing-jokes-didnt-make-cut/"}],"title":"5 Marketing Jokes That Didn't Make The Cut | The PM Group","metaDesc":"Some marketing jokes really make you laugh. These are not those. Here are some of the worst marketing jokes that are so bad they're funny.","focuskw":"marketing jokes","metaKeywords":"","metaRobotsNoindex":"index","metaRobotsNofollow":"follow","opengraphTitle":"5 Marketing Jokes That Didn't Make The Cut | The PM Group","opengraphDescription":"Some marketing jokes really make you laugh. These are not those. Here are some of the worst marketing jokes that are so bad they're funny.","opengraphImage":{"altText":"National Joke Day 2017","sourceUrl":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/joke-day-square.png","srcSet":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/joke-day-square-300x300.png 300w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/joke-day-square-150x150.png 150w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/joke-day-square-768x768.png 768w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/joke-day-square.png 800w"},"twitterTitle":"","twitterDescription":"","twitterImage":null,"canonical":"/5-marketing-jokes-didnt-make-cut/","cornerstone":false,"schema":{"raw":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@graph\":[{\"@type\":\"WebSite\",\"@id\":\"/#website\",\"url\":\"/\",\"name\":\"The PM Group\",\"description\":\"San Antonio\\u2019s Largest Advertising and Marketing Agency\",\"potentialAction\":[{\"@type\":\"SearchAction\",\"tar